Description

Provides methods for interacting with the enquiry database.
FilePath
Interface containing constants for file paths used in the BTO system.
Filter
Interface representing filter functionality for projects.

MainMenuController
Controller that handles the main flow of the system from the main menu to the user-specific menu and actions based on login and role.
Manager
Represents a Manager who is responsible for managing projects, approving or rejecting applications, and handling enquiries in the system.
ManagerActionHandler
Handles the actions performed by a Manager in the system.
ManagerProjectService
A service class that handles various project-related operations for managers.
Officer
The Officer class represents a user with officer privileges who can manage and register for HDB projects.
OfficerActionHandler
This class handles the actions performed by an Officer user in the system.
OfficerApplication
Represents an application made by an officer for a specific project.
OfficerApplicationDatabase
Provides methods for interacting with the officer application database.
PasswordHasher
Utility class for hashing and verifying passwords using SHA-256.
PasswordReset
Interface for handling password reset functionality for a user.
Project
Represents a project that is available for application by eligible applicants.

Controller class for managing projects, staff, and eligibility checks.
ProjectDatabase
Provides methods for interacting with the project database.
RegistrationFailedException
Custom exception thrown when a user fails to complete the registration process after a defined number of invalid input attempts.
Role
Enum representing different roles in the system.
User
Abstract class representing a user in the system.
UserDatabase

View
The View class is responsible for presenting various user interfaces to interact with the system.
